        "Add CloudFront API response caching on GET /gallery and GET /design/:id routes (TTL-controlled)",
        "Add X-Ray tracing across Lambda→DynamoDB→external-API hops for latency debugging",
        "Add CloudWatch Dashboard: p50/p99 latency, error rate, throttle count, cache hit ratio",
        "Upgrade SNS alerts to include Slack webhook subscription on critical alarms"
      ],
      "tradeoffs": [
        "DAX adds ~$0 idle floor (smallest node is always-on); justified only if gallery cache-miss rate causes DynamoDB cost concern",
        "DAX requires Lambda in VPC OR DAX public endpoint (deprecated) — if Lambda is kept outside VPC, use a VPC endpoint + DAX subnet; small NAT cost re-introduced for that Lambda if needed (documented tradeoff)",
        "Still single-region: no cross-region DR; a regional AWS outage causes full outage",
        "CloudFront API caching requires careful cache-key design (exclude auth headers on public routes) — misconfiguration can serve stale operator-hidden designs"
      ],
